variables.value:
Schedule Focus Time Below 

Selecting an option below will try to schedule that much focus time (if available) for you today to work on these tasks. Because we're looking for time during your current day, you can only select an option once within 10 hours of receiving this email.

Personalize_-_Do_you_want_to_be_prompted.description: Set this value to 'yes' if you want the option to book focus time when no focus time is already booked on your calendar. Set value in lowercase - yes/no

Personalize_-_Do_you_want_to_add_tasks_t.description: Do you want the tasks to be added to the focus time events already present on your calendar? Set value in lowercase - yes/no

Personalize_-_What_is_your_time_zone_(Se.description: Paste "Name Of Time Zone" from table here - aka.ms/flowtimezone - and remove any periods '.' from the name.
